models.model_densenet21 module¶

Returns ResNet-16-like model FC (Dense) layers are omitted for fully convolutional layers MaxPooling layers are omitted to retain resolution Using LeakyReLU instead of ReLU Using BatchNormalization (use_bias is thus set to False) Number of kernels is scaled down by 8 Number of Dense units is scaled down by 64

models.model_vgg16 module¶

Returns VGG-16-like model, orignally intended for input size of 224x224x3. FC (Dense) layers from VGG-16 are omitted for fully convolutional layers. Using LeakyReLU instead of ReLU. Using BatchNormalization (use_bias is thus set to False) Number of kernels is scaled down by 8 Number of Dense units is scaled down by 64
